### Variables
@base = http://localhost:9001
@token = Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzUxMiJ9..tQw7dCTF9V-8TvPWWSdFGRjRR7_5pq6sU30OEQmBXdymtCN1400U6LJwPqkG8yZAzAjzkIVrn7B4A8DhXPgE-Q

### Crear contrato
POST {{base}}/api/contracts
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number": "CONT-EPS-2024-001",
  "payerId": 3,
  "paymentModalityId": 11,
  "rateScheduleId": 1,
  "subject": "Prestación de servicios de salud",
  "validFrom": "2024-01-01",
  "validUntil": "2024-12-31",
  "contractValue": 500000000.00,
  "monthlyLimit": 50000000.00,
  "observations": "Contrato principal EPS Sura"
}

###

### Obtener por ID
GET {{base}}/api/contracts/2
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Listar
POST {{base}}/api/contracts/list
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "page": 0,
  "rows": 10,
  "search": "",
  "order_by": "c.numero",
  "order": "ASC"
}

###

### Actualizar
PUT {{base}}/api/contracts/2
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentModalityId": 11,
  "rateScheduleId": 1,
  "subject": "Prestación de servicios de salud - actualizado",
  "validFrom": "2024-01-01",
  "validUntil": "2025-12-31",
  "contractValue": 600000000.00,
  "monthlyLimit": 55000000.00,
  "observations": "Contrato renovado"
}

###

### Activar/Inactivar
PATCH {{base}}/api/contracts/1/toggle-active
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### --- Tarifas del contrato ---

### Agregar tarifa específica
POST {{base}}/api/contracts/2/rates
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "healthServiceId": 3,
  "value": 28000.00,
  "discountPercentage": 5.00,
  "validFrom": "2024-01-01",
  "validUntil": "2024-12-31",
  "observations": "Tarifa negociada con EPS Sura"
}

###

### Listar tarifas del contrato
GET {{base}}/api/contracts/2/rates
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Obtener tarifa por ID
GET {{base}}/api/contracts/2/rates/1
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Actualizar tarifa
PUT {{base}}/api/contracts/2/rates/1
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": 30000.00,
  "discountPercentage": 0.00,
  "validFrom": "2024-01-01",
  "validUntil": "2025-12-31",
  "observations": "Ajuste por IPC"
}

###

### Eliminar tarifa
DELETE {{base}}/api/contracts/1/rates/1
Authorization: {{token}}
